#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:565(command)
msgid "sudo /etc/init.d/saslauthd start"
msgstr "sudo /etc/init.d/saslauthd start"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:567(para)
msgid ""
"<application>Exim4</application> is now configured with SMTP-AUTH using TLS "
"and SASL authentication."
msgstr ""
"<application>Exim4</application> está ahora configurada con SMTP-AUTH usando "
"autenticación TLS y SASL."

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:573(title)
msgid "Dovecot Server"
msgstr "Servidor Dovecot"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:574(para)
msgid ""
"<application>Dovecot</application> is a Mail Delivery Agent, written with "
"security primarily in mind. It supports the major mailbox formats: mbox or "
"Maildir. This section explain how to set it up as an imap or pop3 server."
msgstr ""
"<application>Dovecot</application> es un Agente de Entrega de Correo, "
"escrito con la mirada puesta en la seguridad. Soporta los principales "
"formatos de buzones: mbox o Maildir. Esta sección explica cómo configurar un "
"servidor imap o pop3."

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:582(para)
msgid ""
"To install <application>dovecot</application>, run the following command in "
"the command prompt:"
msgstr ""
"Para instalar<application>dovecot</application>, ejecute la siguiente orden "
"en un terminal:"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:587(command)
msgid "sudo apt-get install dovecot-imapd dovecot-pop3d"
msgstr "sudo apt-get install dovecot-imapd dovecot-pop3d"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:592(para)
msgid ""
"To configure <application>dovecot</application>, you can edit the file "
"<filename>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</filename>. You can choose the protocol "
"you use. It could be pop3, pop3s (pop3 secure), imap and imaps (imap "
"secure). A description of these protocols is beyond the scope of this guide. "
"For further information, refer to the wikipedia articles on <ulink "
"url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/POP3\">POP3</ulink> and <ulink "
"url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_Message_Access_Protocol\">IMAP</u"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Para configurar <application>dovecot</application>, puede editar el archivo "
"<filename>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</filename>. Puede elegir el protocolo "
"que va a usar, que puede ser pop3, pop3s (pop3 seguro), imap e imaps (imap "
"seguro). Una descripción de tales protocolos queda fuera del alcance de esta "
"guía. Para más información, consulte los artículos de la Wikipedia en <ulink "
"url=\"http://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/POP3\">POP3</ulink> y <ulink "
"url=\"http://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_Message_Access_Protocol\">IMAP</u"
"link>."

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:602(para)
msgid ""
"IMAPS and POP3S are more secure that the simple IMAP and POP3 because they "
"use SSL encryption to connect. Once you have chosen the protocol, amend the "
"following line in the file <filename>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</filename>:"
msgstr ""
"IMAPS y POP3S son más seguros que los simples IMAP y POP3 porque usan "
"encriptación SSL para conectarse. Una vez que elija el protocolo, corrija la "
"siguiente línea en el archivo <filename>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</filename>:"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:608(programlisting)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"protocols = pop3 pop3s imap imaps\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"protocols = pop3 pop3s imap imaps\n"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:611(para)
msgid ""
"Next, choose the mailbox you would like to use. "
"<application>Dovecot</application> supports <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">maildir</emphasis> and <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">mbox</emphasis> formats. These are the most commonly used "
"mailbox formats. They both have their own benefits and are discussed on "
"<ulink url=\"http://wiki.dovecot.org/MailboxFormat\">the dovecot "
"website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Después, elija el buzón de correo que desea usar. "
"<application>Dovecot</application> acepta los formatos <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">maildir</emphasis> y <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">mbox</emphasis>. Estos son los formatos de buzón de correo "
"más usados comúnmente. Ambos tienen sus propios beneficios y se discuten en "
"<ulink url=\"http://wiki.dovecot.org/MailboxFormat\">el sitio web de "
"dovecot</ulink>."

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:619(para)
msgid ""
"Once you have chosen your mailbox type, edit the file "
"<filename>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</filename> and change the following line:"
msgstr ""
"Una vez elegido su tipo de buzón de correo, edite el archivo "
"<filename>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</filename> y cambie la siguiente línea:"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:624(programlisting)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"mail_location = maildir:~/Maildir # (for maildir)\n"
"or\n"
"mail_location = mbox:~/mail:INBOX=/var/spool/mail/%u # (for mbox)\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"mail_location = maildir:~/Maildir # (para maildir)\n"
"or\n"
"mail_location = mbox:~/mail:INBOX=/var/spool/mail/%u # (para mbox)\n"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:630(para)
msgid ""
"You should configure your Mail Transport Agent (MTA) to transfer the "
"incoming mail to this type of mailbox if it is different from the one you "
"have configured."
msgstr ""
"Deberá configurar su Agente de Transporte de Correo (Mail Transport Agent, "
"MTA) para poder enviar el correo entrante a este tipo de buzón si resulta "
"ser distinto al que ha configurado."

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:636(para)
msgid ""
"Once you have configured dovecot, restart the "
"<application>dovecot</application> daemon in order to test your setup:"
msgstr ""
"Una vez configurado dovecot, reinicie el demonio "
"<application>dovecot</application> para probar su configuración:"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:641(para)
msgid ""
"If you have enabled imap, or pop3, you can also try to log in with the "
"commands <command>telnet localhost pop3</command> or <command>telnet "
"localhost imap2</command>. If you see something like the following, the "
"installation has been successful:"
msgstr ""
"Si usted ha habilitado imap, o pop3, usted puede probar conectarse con los "
"comandos <command>telnet localhost pop3</command> o <command>telnet "
"localhost imap2</command>. Si usted ve algo parecido a lo siguiente, la "
"instalación ha sido satisfactoria:"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:648(programlisting)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"bhuvan@rainbow:~$ telnet localhost pop3\n"
"Trying 127.0.0.1...\n"
"Connected to localhost.localdomain.\n"
"Escape character is '^]'.\n"
"+OK Dovecot ready.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"bhuvan@rainbow:~$ telnet localhost pop3\n"
"Trying 127.0.0.1...\n"
"Connected to localhost.localdomain.\n"
"Escape character is '^]'.\n"
"+OK Dovecot ready.\n"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:657(title)
msgid "Dovecot SSL Configuration"
msgstr "Configuración de Dovecot SSL"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:658(para)
msgid ""
"To configure <application>dovecot</application> to use SSL, you can edit the "
"file <filename>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</filename> and amend following "
"lines:"
msgstr ""
"Para configurar <application>dovecot</application> para que utilice SSL, "
"usted puede editar el archivo <filename>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</filename> "
"y corregir las siguientes líneas:"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:663(programlisting)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"ssl_cert_file = /etc/ssl/certs/ssl-cert-snakeoil.pem\n"
"ssl_key_file = /etc/ssl/private/ssl-cert-snakeoil.key\n"
"ssl_disable = no\n"
"disable_plaintext_auth = no\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"ssl_cert_file = /etc/ssl/certs/ssl-cert-snakeoil.pem\n"
"ssl_key_file = /etc/ssl/private/ssl-cert-snakeoil.key\n"
"ssl_disable = no\n"
"disable_plaintext_auth = no\n"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:669(para)
msgid ""
"You can get the SSL certificate from a Certificate Issuing Authority or you "
"can create self signed SSL certificate. The latter is a good option for "
"email, because SMTP clients rarely complain about \"self-signed "
"certificates\". Please refer to <xref linkend=\"certificates-and-"
"security\"/> for details about how to create self signed SSL certificate. "
"Once you create the certificate, you will have a key file and a certificate "
"file. Please copy them to the location pointed in the "
"<filename>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</filename> configuration file."
msgstr ""
"Puede obtener el certificado SSL a través de una Autoridad emisora de "
"certificados o puede crear un certificado SSL autofirmado. Este último es "
"una buena opción para correo electrónico, ya que los clientes SMTP rara vez "
"se quejan por \"certificados autofirmados\". Por favor diríjase a <xref "
"linkend=\"certificates-and-security\"/> para obtener más detalles acerca de "
"cómo crear certificados SSL autofirmados. Una vez haya creado el "
"certificado, tendrá un archivo de clave y un archivo de certificado. "
"Cópielos a la ubicación indicada en el archivo de configuración "
"<filename>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</filename>."

