#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:1285(para)
msgid ""
"Bouncing spam can be a bad idea as the return address is often faked. "
"Consider editing <filename>/etc/amavis/conf.d/20-debian_defaults</filename> "
"to set <emphasis>$final_spam_destiny</emphasis> to D_DISCARD rather than "
"D_BOUNCE, as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Rebotar correo basura puede ser una mala idea ya que la dirección de retorno "
"casi siempre es falsa. Considere editar <filename>/etc/amavis/conf.d/20-"
"debian_defaults</filename> para poner "
"<emphasis>$final_spam_destiny</emphasis> en D_DISCARD en lugar de D_BOUNCE, "
"así:"

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:1290(programlisting)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"$final_spam_destiny       = D_DISCARD;\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"$final_spam_destiny       = D_DISCARD;\n"

